expression.expression-string: int mid = (start+end)/2; int check = unsortedList.get(mid); if (check == value){ return mid; } else if(check < value) { return searchingForIndex(value,start,end=mid-1); } else if (check > value){ return searchingForIndex(value,start=mid+1,end); } return mid; }
